OL,6,FA gunman who shot a landlady after she
OL,7,Fintervened in a row outside her pub
OL,8,Fshouted "I want to apologise to you"
OL,9,Fas he was jailed for the attack.
OL,11,FBonita Page, 56, was outside The Red
OL,12,FLion in Wath upon Dearne, South
OL,13,FYorkshire, when Oliver Corney fired
OL,14,Fthree times into a group of people on
OL,15,F28 June last year.
OL,17,FMrs Page was hit in the leg and
OL,18,Fsuffered "life-changing" injuries in
OL,19,Fthe incident, Judge Jeremy Richardson
OL,20,FKC told Sheffield Crown Court on
OL,21,FFriday.
