OL,6,FJudge Richardson told Corney he had
OL,7,F"narrowly avoided" a life sentence as
OL,8,Fhe jailed him for 11 years and nine
OL,9,Fmonths, with an extended licence
OL,10,Fperiod of five years.
OL,12,FAs he was led from the dock the
OL,13,Fdefendant shouted: "Mrs Page, I want
OL,14,Fto apologise to you."
OL,16,FThe judge told the court how Mrs Page
OL,17,Fhad intervened in an argument earlier
OL,18,Fin the evening, which he said was
OL,19,Fprobably to do with drugs.
